{"id":154,"date":"2013-07-04T21:58:25","date_gmt":"2013-07-04T16:28:25","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/?p=154"},"modified":"2017-06-22T15:42:11","modified_gmt":"2017-06-22T10:12:11","slug":"chat-with-your-google-contacts-from-outlook-com","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/2013\/07\/04\/chat-with-your-google-contacts-from-outlook-com\/","title":{"rendered":"Chat with your Google contacts from Outlook.com"},"content":{"rendered":"<aside class=\"mashsb-container mashsb-main mashsb-stretched\"><div class=\"mashsb-box\"><div class=\"mashsb-count mash-large\" style=\"float:left;\"><div class=\"counts mashsbcount\">97<\/div><span class=\"mashsb-sharetext\">SHARES<\/span><\/div><div class=\"mashsb-buttons\"><a class=\"mashicon-facebook mash-large mash-center mashsb-noshadow\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwordpress%2Findex.php%2F2013%2F07%2F04%2Fchat-with-your-google-contacts-from-outlook-com%2F\" target=\"_top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"icon\"><\/span><span class=\"text\">&nbsp;Tell&nbsp;your&nbsp;friends&nbsp;<\/span><\/a><a class=\"mashicon-twitter mash-large mash-center mashsb-noshadow\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/intent\/tweet?text=&url=http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/2013\/07\/04\/chat-with-your-google-contacts-from-outlook-com\/&via=Sourav_Ghosh\" target=\"_top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"icon\"><\/span><span class=\"text\">&nbsp;Tweet&nbsp;about&nbsp;this&nbsp;<\/span><\/a><div class=\"onoffswitch2 mash-large mashsb-noshadow\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div><\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                <div style=\"clear:both;\"><\/div><div class=\"mashsb-toggle-container\"><\/div><\/aside>\n            <!-- Share buttons by mashshare.net - Version: 3.7.7--><p>Email used to be once a very important part of what we called the Internet. And it is indeed one of the essence of this vast network, which still holds much importance even today when many of us are more comfortable sending short pieces of information via IM services and direct messaging clients like Facebook, BBM, and WhatsApp! Keeping this in mind, many software giants are providing chat clients embedded into their web-based email services. Google recently introduced Hangouts which replaces the older Google Talk; Microsoft recently started retiring its Messenger client, merging it with Skype; Yahoo! provides Yahoo! messenger, and so on.<\/p>\n<p>Till a few days ago, Outlook.com, the renovated Hotmail service, used to allow users to chat with Messenger and Facebook contacts. Recently, the ability to chat with Google contacts was added. So, if you want to chat with your contacts on your Google account from Outlook.com,<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<p>here\u2019s how it is:<a href=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-1.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-0\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"background-image: none; float: right; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-width: 0px;\" title=\"Messaging (1)\" src=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-1_thumb.png\" alt=\"Messaging (1)\" width=\"244\" height=\"111\" align=\"right\" border=\"0\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u00b7 Open Outlook.com on your favourite browser.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>\u00b7 Click on the Smiley icon at the top-right corner.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>\u00b7 If you haven\u2019t already, you\u2019ll get an option to add your Google contacts. Click on that.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-2.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-1\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"background-image: none; float: none; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin-left: auto; display: block; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: auto; border-width: 0px;\" title=\"Messaging (2)\" src=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-2_thumb.png\" alt=\"Messaging (2)\" width=\"244\" height=\"143\" border=\"0\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u00b7 Confirm your action from Microsoft\u2019s prompt and then from Google\u2019s prompt.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-3.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-2\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"background-image: none; float: left; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 40px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-width: 0px;\" title=\"Messaging (3)\" src=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-3_thumb.png\" alt=\"Messaging (3)\" width=\"244\" height=\"172\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" \/><\/a><a href=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-4.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-3\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"background-image: none; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 40px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-width: 0px;\" title=\"Messaging (4)\" src=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-4_thumb.png\" alt=\"Messaging (4)\" width=\"244\" height=\"193\" border=\"0\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u00b7 That\u2019s it! You\u2019ll get a confirmation message saying that your accounts are connected.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-5.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-4\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"background-image: none; float: none; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin-left: auto; display: block; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: auto; border-width: 0px;\" title=\"Messaging (5)\" src=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-5_thumb.png\" alt=\"Messaging (5)\" width=\"244\" height=\"118\" border=\"0\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>If you want to disconnect in future, that\u2019s quite easy too! Also, you can control your online visibility for Google contacts in just two clicks.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-7.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox-image-5\" data-rl_title=\"\" data-rl_caption=\"\" title=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"background-image: none; float: none; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin-left: auto; display: block; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: auto; border-width: 0px;\" title=\"Messaging (7)\" src=\"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/Messaging-7_thumb.png\" alt=\"Messaging (7)\" width=\"244\" height=\"214\" border=\"0\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Will you be using this to chat with your friends? Tell us in comments.<\/p>\n<aside class=\"mashsb-container mashsb-main mashsb-stretched\"><div class=\"mashsb-box\"><div class=\"mashsb-count mash-large\" style=\"float:left;\"><div class=\"counts mashsbcount\">97<\/div><span class=\"mashsb-sharetext\">SHARES<\/span><\/div><div class=\"mashsb-buttons\"><a class=\"mashicon-facebook mash-large mash-center mashsb-noshadow\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwordpress%2Findex.php%2F2013%2F07%2F04%2Fchat-with-your-google-contacts-from-outlook-com%2F\" target=\"_top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"icon\"><\/span><span class=\"text\">&nbsp;Tell&nbsp;your&nbsp;friends&nbsp;<\/span><\/a><a class=\"mashicon-twitter mash-large mash-center mashsb-noshadow\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/intent\/tweet?text=&url=http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/2013\/07\/04\/chat-with-your-google-contacts-from-outlook-com\/&via=Sourav_Ghosh\" target=\"_top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"icon\"><\/span><span class=\"text\">&nbsp;Tweet&nbsp;about&nbsp;this&nbsp;<\/span><\/a><div class=\"onoffswitch2 mash-large mashsb-noshadow\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div><\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                <div style=\"clear:both;\"><\/div><div class=\"mashsb-toggle-container\"><\/div><\/aside>\n            <!-- Share buttons by mashshare.net - Version: 3.7.7-->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Email used to be once a very important part of what we called the Internet. And it is indeed one of the essence of this vast network, which still holds much importance even today when many of us are more comfortable sending short pieces of information via IM services and direct messaging clients like Facebook, &hellip; <\/p>\n<p class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/2013\/07\/04\/chat-with-your-google-contacts-from-outlook-com\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> &#8220;Chat with your Google contacts from Outlook.com&#8221;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":156,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[41],"tags":[71,141,231],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/154"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=154"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/154\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7381,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/154\/revisions\/7381"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/156"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=154"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/loc